text: Krasny Voskhod () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Krasnovoskhodsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 842 as of 2010. There are 13 streets. == Geography == It is located 85 km from Iglino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Krasny Voskhod, Iglinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
